St. John Burnham is Singe 'n' Burn is the headmaster at the Prince of Wales school. An Englishman, he is known for choosing six boys from the third form each year to take under his personal tutelage and mold into "Renaissance men." Singe 'n' Burn assists Peekay and Morrie with setting up the night school for black boxers, but only after he has met Gideon Mandoma.